  <h1>
   gxc_pause_movie_recording
  </h1>
  This function is used to pause a GXC recording that was previously started with
  <span>
   <a href="gxc_start_movie_recording.htm">
    gxc_start_movie_recording()
   </a>
  </span>
  .
  <h4>
   Syntax:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">gxc_pause_movie_recording();
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   Returns:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">N/A
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   Example:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">if (keyboard_check_pressed(vk_escape))
{
    gxc_pause_movie_recording();
}
</code></pre>
  This will pause the GXC movie recording if the escape key is pressed.
